article.headline: Amarri Tice scores 20, grabs 13 rebounds to lead Quinnipiac over Rider 72-67
article.description: — Amarri Tice finished with 20 points and 13 rebounds to help Quinnipiac defeat Rider 72-67 on Friday night.
article.linkText: Amarri Tice scores 20, grabs 13 rebounds to lead Quinnipiac over Rider 72-67
article.story: LAWRENCEVILLE, N.J. -- — Amarri Tice finished with 20 points and 13 rebounds to help Quinnipiac defeat Rider 72-67 on Friday night. Khaden Bennett had 12 points for the Bobcats (4-5, 1-0 Metro Atlantic Athletic Conference). Paul Otieno pitched in with 11 points, seven rebounds and four blocks. Zion Cruz led the Broncs (4-6, 0-2) with 15 points. Tariq Ingraham added 11 points and 10 rebounds, while Jay Alvarez had 11 points and two steals. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
